# Landing Site (sharppicks.ai)

## Location
Static landing site files live in `/landing` directory.

## Deployment
- Hosted on Cloudflare Pages (project: sharppicks)
- Domain: sharppicks.ai, sharppicks.pages.dev
- Root directory: /landing
- No Git auto-deploy -- requires manual deploy
- No build step needed (static HTML)
- Deploy command: npx wrangler pages deploy landing/ --project-name sharppicks

## Structure
- /landing/index.html — main landing page
- /landing/support/ — support page
- /landing/sitemap.xml — SEO sitemap
- /landing/robots.txt — crawler directives
- /landing/_headers — Cloudflare security + cache headers
- /landing/_redirects — www redirect, /app redirect
- /landing/assets/ — CSS, JS, images

## SEO
- OG meta tags and Twitter Card tags on index.html
- JSON-LD structured data on index.html
- Default OG image: /landing/assets/images/og-default.png (1200x630)
- Sitemap includes all public pages
- Canonical URL: https://sharppicks.ai/
